These are Puzzles for 1x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-1::.
City: nizza, new-york, marseilles, rome, san-francisco
1. the person traveling to rome is in the middle##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
3. the person traveling to marseilles is in an odd position##4
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2  |   3   |   4   |  5  |
| City   | marseilles | nizza | rome | new-york | san-francisco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-2::.
5 different games are played: poker, monopoly, billiard, whist, bridge
1. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
2. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
3. the person playing monopoly is in an odd position##4
4. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
5. the person playing monopoly is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2  |     3     |     4     |     5      |
| Game   | whist | bridge | monopoly | poker | billiard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: aconite, iris, bellflower, amaryllis, lily
1. the person who growsiris is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3
3. the person who growsaconite is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growslily is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |  3   |     4      |   5   |
| Flower   | iris | bellflower | aconite | amaryllis | lily |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-4::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, pall-mall, vegafina, swisher, fonseca
1. the aristoff-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
3. the swisher-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left or right of the swisher-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |       1       |     2     |       3        |   4    |     5     |
| Cigar   | swisher | pall-mall | vegafina | fonseca | aristoff |

