2. the french is on the left of the spanish##1
3. the indonesian is on the right of the italian##1
4. the italian is on the right of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |  2   |     3     |     4     |    5    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | french | spanish | italian | indonesian |

