2. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |     2      |   3   |    4     |    5    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | coffee | juice | cola | hot-chocolate |

