2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |  3   |     4     |    5    |
| Sport   | climbing | water-polo | weightlifting | snowboarding | parkour |

