.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-9::.
House: cottage, tower, wooden, victorian, art-deco
1. the cottage house is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
2. the art-deco house is on the far left or far right##3
3. the tower house is on the right of the wooden house##1
4. the cottage house is on the right of the tower house##1
5. the tower house is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
6. the cottage house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |   2   |   3   |  4   |     5      |
| House   | art-deco | wooden | tower | cottage | victorian |

