.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-11::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: subway, bus, car, snowmobile, quad-bike
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the bus and the person driving the quad-bike##2
4. the person driving the snowmobile is in the middle##1
5. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4     |   5    |
| Transport   | car | bus | snowmobile | quad-bike | subway |

