2. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |   2    |     3     |   4   |     5     |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | chess | photography | board-games | card-games |

