.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-14::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, april, january, october, august
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is in the middle##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |  3   |   4    |     5     |
| Birthday   | january | august | october | april | february |

