.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: disco, jazz, trance, metal, punk
1. the fan of punk is between the fan of jazz and the fan of trance##2
2. the fan of metal is in an even position##4
3. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of punk##1
4. the fan of trance is between the fan of punk and the fan of metal##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2  |    3     |    4     |   5    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | punk | trance | metal | disco |

 